When I say this OpenAI API-compatible endpoint, I don't necessarily mean that the model is like an OpenAI model, a GPT-5 or something like that.

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:28.000
What I mean is that a few years ago, when OpenAI was like kind of the first big player that made this splash with the first release of chat GPT,

00:34:28.000 --> 00:34:35.000
they also made that model accessible via this API called the V1 Completions API.

00:34:35.000 --> 00:34:47.000
